<l>poruḷkaruvi kālam viṉaiyiṭaṉō ṭaintu </l>
<l>miruṭīra veṇṇic ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do an act after a due consideration of the (following) five, viz money, means, time, execution and place</l>
